has x and y coordinates
has orientation (in radians)
has hitcircle radius
has a movement vector

must implement a 'draw' method which would otherwise draw the entity centered on (0,0) facing direction 0
must implement an 'act' method which will take care of all upkeep/actions an entity does each game tick
uses translate and rotate along with save and restore state to render
comes with a builtin 'render' method which will save the current canvas state, apply translations/rotations, call draw, and restore the previous canvas state

calculates collisions in terms of circular collisions
